data.description: Experience the perfect blend of historic charm and contemporary comfort in this meticulously maintained townhome. Step inside to discover tiled baths and a granite kitchen counter complemented by 43" cabinets, seamlessly marrying classic aesthetics with modern convenience. A two-way gas log fireplace adorned with stone antique mantels serves as the focal point, gracefully connecting the living and dining rooms. Off-street parking adds practicality to the charm. The spacious master bath boasts a washer and dryer for added convenience. Rarely do properties with three bedrooms and three baths become available in Olde Towne! Seize this opportunity to own a piece of history with all the comforts of today.
